item.description:
Hello PP2012 People!

 

We are going to look at our 6th and 7 month goals and reevaluate where we are. Everyone should check in with themselves and see how you are doing. Let's discuss at the meeting and talk it through.

 

Please bring any part of your projects you would like to share and get feedback on.

 

We meet on the 16th at 7pm at Jeff's Studio. I look forward to seeing your progress. We will discuss any challenges you may have encountered putting your goals into writing and we will have time to brain storm ways to help you with your challenges. Please keep an open mind.

Cheers,

Donna
item.how_to_find_us: Walk in the room to the right as you enter from the parking lot.
